---- 10000 Reasons
# 10000 Reasons
--- Chorus
Bless the Lord, O my soul
O my soul
worship His holy Name
Sing like never before
O my soul
I’ll worship Your holy Name
--- Verse 1
The sun comes up
it’s a new day dawning
**
It’s time to sing 
Your song again
**
Whatever may pass 
and whatever lies before me
**
Let me be singing 
when the evening comes
**
--- Verse 2
You’re rich in love 
and You’re slow to anger
**
Your Name is great 
and Your heart is kind
**
For all Your goodness 
I will keep on singing
**
Ten thousand reasons 
for my heart to find
**
--- Verse 3
And on that day 
when my strength is failing
**
The end draws near 
and my time has come
**
Still my soul sings 
Your praise unending
**
Ten thousand years 
and then forevermore
***
---- 深触我心 How Precious You are to Me
# 深触我心 ## How Precious You are to Me
--- Verse
耶稣 诚然担当
我们的忧患 背负我们痛苦
耶稣 为我们的过犯受害
为我们的罪孽压伤
--- Pre-Chorus
因祢受的刑罚 
我们得平安
因祢受的鞭伤 
我们得医治 完全得医治
--- Chorus
感谢耶稣 我的救主
我得平安 我得医治
我的耶稣 爱我的主
祢的恩典 深触我心
***
---- 我多么需要有祢 I really need you
# 我多么需要有祢 ## I really need you
--- verse 1
我多么需要有祢 
有祢天天与我亲近
我时刻不能忘记 
是祢赐我每个气息
--- verse 2
我多么需要有祢 
有祢天天领我前行
我时刻不能忘记 
是祢掌管我的生命
--- chorus
缤纷的世界 夺不去我的眼
我要定睛在祢荣面
因为离了祢 
就像风筝断了线
飘落在天地之间
**
忙碌的生活 夺不去我的心
我要安静在祢面前
因为祢同在 
是我一生的等候
是我一生的寻求
**
***